wiki.summary: Breathe showcases Yeat’s unapologetic attitude and hunger for success. Produced by ​bart how, the song exudes a relentless energy as Yeat boasts about his financial achievements and dismisses anyone who gets in his way. The chorus emphasizes his disregard for others' opinions and his relentless drive to succeed, while the verses delve into his confidence and determination to rise above the rest. With its aggressive delivery and bold lyrics, “Breathe” captures Yeat’s uncompromising pursuit of greatness in the face of any obstacle. Read more on Last.fm.
